## 🔗 API ROUTES

| Method | Route | Purpose |
|--------|-------|---------|
| POST | `/api/auth/signup` | Register new user |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login user |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |
| GET/POST/PUT/DELETE | `/api/products` | Product CRUD |
| GET/POST/PUT | `/api/floors` | Floor & Table management |
| POST | `/api/sessions/open` | Open POS session |
| POST | `/api/sessions/close` | Close POS session |
| GET | `/api/sessions` | List sessions |
| POST | `/api/orders` | Create order |
| PUT | `/api/orders/:id` | Update order |
| PUT | `/api/orders/:id/send-kitchen` | Send to kitchen |
| PUT | `/api/orders/:id/kitchen-status` | Update kitchen status |
| PUT | `/api/orders/:id/pay` | Process payment |
| GET/PUT | `/api/payment-methods` | Payment config |
| GET | `/api/reports/sales` | Sales reports |
| GET | `/api/reports/sessions` | Session reports |
| GET | `/api/reports/products` | Product reports |
| POST | `/api/self-order/token` | Generate self-order token |
| POST | `/api/self-order/place` | Place self-order |

---

## 📄 PAGE LIST & ROUTES

| # | Page | Route | Description |
|---|------|-------|-------------|
| 1 | **Login** | `/login` | Email + password login |
| 2 | **Signup** | `/signup` | New user registration |
| 3 | **Dashboard** | `/dashboard` | Sales overview + charts + KPIs |
| 4 | **Products** | `/backend/products` | Product CRUD management |
| 5 | **Payment Methods** | `/backend/payments` | Enable/disable + UPI config |
| 6 | **Floor Plan** | `/backend/floors` | Manage floors & tables |
| 7 | **POS Terminal** | `/backend/pos-terminal` | Session management |
| 8 | **Self Ordering** | `/backend/self-ordering` | Token generation |
| 9 | **Floor View (POS)** | `/pos/floor` | Select table to start order |
| 10 | **Order Screen** | `/pos/order/:tableId` | Product selection + cart |
| 11 | **Payment Screen** | `/pos/payment/:orderId` | Payment method + process |
| 12 | **UPI QR Screen** | `/pos/payment/:orderId/upi` | QR code display |
| 13 | **Kitchen Display** | `/kitchen` | Real-time order board |
| 14 | **Customer Display** | `/customer/:orderId` | Order & payment status |
| 15 | **Reports** | `/reports` | Filtered reports + export |

