## 🌟 INNOVATION DIFFERENTIATORS (What Makes Us WIN)

### vs Other 102 Teams:
1. **Real-time Kitchen Sync** — Socket.io powered, not just CRUD
2. **Live Customer Display** — separate URL, real-time updates
3. **UPI QR Generation** — actual QR code from UPI ID, not fake
4. **Self-Ordering Token** — mobile ordering without an app
5. **3-Stage Kitchen Board** — Kanban-style (To Cook → Preparing → Completed)
6. **Premium Dark/Light Mode** — not just color swap, full design system
7. **Export Reports** — PDF & XLS, production-ready
8. **Session-based POS** — proper POS session lifecycle
9. **Table Status Sync** — occupied/available/reserved in real-time
10. **Order Number System** — auto-generated, tracked across lifecycle

